{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-log-post-jsx","path":"/color-independent-overlay/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>If you don't know the color of the element, for example you have an array of buttons with different colors, you can add a color-independent overlay with box-shadow property.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">button</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--some-color-here<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">button:hover</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">box-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inset 0 0 0 99999px <span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>255<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 255<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 255<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0.2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Add color independent overlay","date":"2021-02-13","tags":["overlay","color","button","css"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/color-independent-overlay/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}